      <title>Image does not show up on Macintosh</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/novenimagecropper/forum/issues/image_does_not_show_up_on_macintosh</link>
      <description>The image uploading interface (as viewed when editing or creating a content item from the admin backend interface) refuses to show the image on a Macintosh.  It appears to be a browser-independent problem, confirmed on Safari and Firefox on the Mac.  After you upload the image, in the place where the image should show, a small blue icon with a question mark appears instead.&#13;
&#13;
eZ Publish version 4.2, novenimagecropper version 1.0.6.&#13;
&#13;
Please help!  Thanks much!</description>
